{"tid":191982,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"法唔法國依個中國自秦朝以來都冇轉變過","createTime":"2017-04-08T09:32:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-16T07:03:40.000Z","uid":70928,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bf4df9f7208ebf2a80ebd9be6afbbd5598d83ff1","tid":191982,"uid":70928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T09:32:27.000Z","msg":"昔日有趙高指鹿為馬 朝臣咐和以免得罪當權者<br />\n<br />\n今日有政府叫市民每日做半個鐘運動解決抑鬱<br />\n<br />\n而唔敢提最高工時 土地居住問題 以免得罪地產商 靠剝削為生既生意人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8f754252e9689f8a3f9de971d06eaa4d5ed1609","tid":191982,"uid":104474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T10:42:31.000Z","msg":"民族性問題 唔識進步 結終儒毒太深"},{"pid":"085c94d0d1076cf10a8b67464c81a0b6454406bc","tid":191982,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T10:54:58.000Z","msg":"所以必須要擺脫中國"},{"pid":"1ab1e1596f482fd9b4fdb13e9483e6d35b78a8f7","tid":191982,"uid":8171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T10:57:36.000Z","msg":"官商鄉黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0f169f6eafb43aa40a4825aee08978bf4208d76","tid":191982,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T10:57:54.000Z","msg":"前390年左右高盧的酋長布倫努斯率軍穿越阿爾卑斯山前往今日之義大利，並在阿里亞河戰役中擊敗羅馬軍隊，侵入羅馬。高盧人的入侵大大削弱羅馬國家的實力，而高盧人對於羅馬地區的支配持續到前345年，當時高盧人與羅馬簽署和平條約。前125年，羅馬征服高盧南部，建立諾斯特拉行省（Provincia Nostra，意為「我們的行省」，此亦為法語「普羅旺斯」的詞源）[29]。 尤利烏斯&middot;凱撒征服高盧全境，並於前52年平息酋長維欽托利的叛亂[30]，此後的奧古斯都將高盧分區建省[31]。許多法國城市皆於此時期建立，包括盧格杜努姆（今里昂）[31]，它是高盧行省的首府以及西部羅馬的最重要城市之一。 這些城市具有濃厚的羅馬風格，建有廣場、劇場、圓形廣場、圓形競技場和早期水療系統（thermal baths）。此後高盧人逐漸羅馬化，汲取羅馬文化習俗、並開始使用羅馬語言（拉丁文是今日法語的始祖）。宗教方面，當時的羅馬與凱爾特的多神論亦出現綜攝現象"},{"pid":"9404927983d55ab1eb2db8fb9f63eab1c9543467","tid":191982,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T10:58:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/4/4e/Prise_de_la_Bastille.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F4%2F4e%2FPrise_de_la_Bastille.jpg&h=94b3993f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"846f55332b8be1bc099e104e9c54a012fad41d41","tid":191982,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T10:59:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d7/France_base_map_18_regions.png/500px-France_base_map_18_regions.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2Fd%2Fd7%2FFrance_base_map_18_regions.png%2F500px-France_base_map_18_regions.png&h=268cfa36&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3996662d4644fee1ea0f52b91cc4ac89d3a5d258","tid":191982,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T11:03:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>民族性問題 唔識進步 結終儒毒太深</blockquote><br />\n秦朝唔係行儒家"},{"pid":"82ce0746eab22218121e45cf0ec54812a9a74e86","tid":191982,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T11:04:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>民族性問題 唔識進步 結終儒毒太深</blockquote><br />\n秦朝唔係行儒家</blockquote><br />\n可以証明支那種自古以來就係大仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2661763692fa857cd52fcf865fe06d0a1e86704","tid":191982,"uid":104474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T15:25:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>民族性問題 唔識進步 結終儒毒太深</blockquote><br />\n秦朝唔係行儒家</blockquote><br />\n 樓主計秦朝都差唔多 收六國皮大一統<br />\n不過結終大一統係必然過程 最仆街都係董仲舒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e800e0be50825c817d4ec1a22fb2e9d7ff9dced","tid":191982,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T15:28:42.000Z","msg":"中華民國北洋政府 時期, 試過有轉變<br />\n當時是中國最自由既時期"},{"pid":"8b97507c38eed48dbc510a006fe39634825ad4b8","tid":191982,"uid":104474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T17:41:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中華民國北洋政府 時期, 試過有轉變<br />\n當時是中國最自由既時期</blockquote><br />\n五四？ 可以詳述下嗎？ 不過有又點？ 一個毛魔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bd71d35a5e04c3d524dfa820878e413184a1e01","tid":191982,"uid":17213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T02:02:28.000Z","msg":"如果他日中國各省分裂求獨立，都只會係戰國時代，軍閥割據，香港命運依然走唔甩。難聽講句，要改變呢個情況，只有民主中國，聯邦制憲先有得救。"},{"pid":"570395b60be404ed1d88d50027123f8168d57400","tid":191982,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T06:13:56.000Z","msg":"幾十個國家，唔同時代，唔同種族，可以炒埋一碟叫中國？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bff3bda17842affbb64101629af1237a81f6a259","tid":191982,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T06:44:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果他日中國各省分裂求獨立，都只會係戰國時代，軍閥割據，香港命運依然走唔甩。難聽講句，要改變呢個情況，只有民主中國，聯邦制憲先有得救。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以中國人內鬥既DNA, 行民主制度, 多黨制<br />\n各黨派都會互相攻伐, 打內戰<br />\n<br />\n最好係香港 好似97年前咁, 由西方國家保護, 同中國隔絕"},{"pid":"8e70e048b4856af0f0639dd9981d89eba0e4d8a2","tid":191982,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T06:44:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾十個國家，唔同時代，唔同種族，可以炒埋一碟叫中國？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n家陣呢個年代<br />\n大把國家都係 由古代幾十國家, 幾十個種族 炒埋一碟嫁啦"},{"pid":"f6411ff5033bb5680f1a1ac41978803e270e8613","tid":191982,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T07:03:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}